          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The documents that govern your use of Splynek. Read once, then scan when something changes.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Die Dokumente, die deine Nutzung von Splynek regeln. Einmal lesen, dann scannen, wenn sich etwas ändert."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los documentos que rigen tu uso de Splynek. Léelos una vez, luego revísalos cuando algo cambie."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les documents qui régissent ton utilisation de Splynek. Lis-les une fois, puis parcours-les quand quelque chose change."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I documenti che regolano l'uso di Splynek. Leggili una volta, poi rivedili quando qualcosa cambia."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Os documentos que regem o teu uso do Splynek. Lê uma vez, depois revê quando algo mudar."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The local LLM didn't know any good European or open-source alternatives. Contribute one at github.com/Splynek/splynek.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Das lokale LLM kannte keine guten europäischen oder Open-Source-Alternativen. Tragen Sie eine auf github.com/Splynek/splynek bei."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El LLM local no conocía buenas alternativas europeas o de código abierto. Contribuye con una en github.com/Splynek/splynek."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le LLM local ne connaissait aucune bonne alternative européenne ou open-source. Contribuez-en une sur github.com/Splynek/splynek."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L’LLM locale non conosceva buone alternative europee o open-source. Contribuiscine una su github.com/Splynek/splynek."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O LLM local não conhecia boas alternativas europeias ou de código aberto. Contribui em github.com/Splynek/splynek."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The local LLM is drafting your recipe. This usually takes 10–60 s on Apple Silicon.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Das lokale LLM erstellt dein Rezept. Das dauert auf Apple Silicon normalerweise 10–60 s."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El LLM local está redactando tu receta. Suele tardar 10–60 s en Apple Silicon."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le LLM local rédige ta recette. Cela prend généralement 10–60 s sur Apple Silicon."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'LLM locale sta redigendo la tua ricetta. Di solito ci vogliono 10–60 s su Apple Silicon."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "O LLM local está a redigir a tua receita. Costuma demorar 10–60 s em Apple Silicon."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The local LLM proposes each download with URL + rationale": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Das lokale LLM schlägt jeden Download mit URL + Begründung vor"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
